# PWA (@ducanh2912/next-pwa)

## Setup (already configured in this project)
- PWA library: `@ducanh2912/next-pwa`. Do NOT suggest Serwist or next-offline.
- `next.config.ts` wraps with `withPWA({ dest: 'public', disable: process.env.NODE_ENV === 'development', ... })`.
  - `disable: true` in dev (otherwise cache hell).
  - `reloadOnOnline: true` is set — do not change without discussion.
- `public/manifest.json` is the static manifest (not a `manifest.ts` route).
- Theme color: `#16a34a` (morning-green-600).
- Required icon sizes: 192x192 and 512x512 with `"purpose": "any maskable"`.

## Manifest fields (must be present)
- `name`: "Morning Glory Academy — SchoolPay"
- `short_name`: "SchoolPay" (≤12 chars ✅)
- `start_url`: "/"
- `display`: "standalone"
- `background_color`: "#ffffff"
- `theme_color`: "#16a34a"

## Network state
- `useOnline()` hook in `hooks/useOnline.ts` listens to `online`/`offline` events.
- Render an unobtrusive banner when offline — never block the UI.
- Every mutation has three UI states: optimistic (immediate), pending-sync
  (queued with sync indicator), failed (with retry).

## Sync
- `useSync()` hook in `hooks/useSync.ts` drives the sync engine on a 60s interval
  when online. Also triggered on manual user actions.
- Sync queue lives in IndexedDB via Dexie (`lib/dexie/`).
- Sync engine: `lib/sync/engine.ts`. Queue processor: `lib/sync/queue.ts`.
- Max 5 attempts per item (`MAX_SYNC_ATTEMPTS` in `lib/constants.ts`).
- `SyncIndicator` component in `components/ui/SyncIndicator.tsx` shows status.

## Offline-first writes
- Write locally to Dexie first. Add to sync queue in the same Dexie transaction.
- UI updates immediately from `useLiveQuery` (optimistic).
- Never block a user action on network availability.
